dct_title_s: L'America divisa ne'suoi principali stati di nuovo projezione
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Shows also the Pacific Ocean to New Zealand. Below title: Venezia 1776. Possibly from Zatta's Atlante novissima. [1788]. Includes text and ill.
